### Misc ###########################################

lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light color (1, 0.8, 0.3)
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light intensity 2.5
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light falloffRate 1.3
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceColor (1, 0.8, 0.3)
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceIntensity 2.5
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceFalloff 3
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceWallIntensityScale 1
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceFloorIntensityScale 1
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage1_light diffusionSourceIsDirectional 0

lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light color (1, 0.8, 0.3)
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light intensity 2.5
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light falloffRate 1.3
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceColor (1, 0.8, 0.3)
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceIntensity 1.6
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceFalloff 3
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceWallIntensityScale 1
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceFloorIntensityScale 1
lightAttribOverride bonfireStage2_light diffusionSourceIsDirectional 0

